Wee haue therefore cauſed all the goods and Marchandizes chargeable with the ſaid poundage either broght in, or tranſported out of this Kingdome, together with the ſeuerall kinds, qualities, numbers, weights, meaſures and contents of the ſame, and the values, prices, and Rates thereof to be particularly entred and expreſſed in this preſent Booke, containing in leaues on both ſides 
                  ••
               to the entent his Maieſtie may henceforth bee iuſtly aunſwered of the ſaid poundage, according to the tenor of the ſaid Act of Parliament;
